749
00:48:32,060 --> 00:48:35,220
 Ti Isuse vidiš u njezinoj okolici,

750
00:48:35,220 --> 00:48:36,340
 njezname životu,

751
00:48:36,340 --> 00:48:38,240
 velike razdore, svađe,

752
00:48:38,840 --> 00:48:39,680
 nepraštanje,

753
00:48:39,680 --> 00:48:40,360
 jedan nered,

754
00:48:40,360 --> 00:48:41,280
 jedan kaos.

755
00:48:41,280 --> 00:48:42,600
 Ja te molim Isuse,

756
00:48:42,600 --> 00:48:43,640
 po ovoj molitvi,

757
00:48:43,640 --> 00:48:45,120
 neka zavlada mir,

758
00:48:45,120 --> 00:48:46,980
