759
00:48:46,980 --> 00:48:48,480
 Ti znaš, Isuse,

760
00:48:48,480 --> 00:48:50,420
 koliko je ovoj ženi teško razumijeti

761
00:48:50,420 --> 00:48:51,700
 zašto toliko zla,

762
00:48:51,700 --> 00:48:53,220
