773
00:49:07,680 --> 00:49:09,860
 Jeste tu?

774
00:49:09,860 --> 00:49:10,140
 Amen.

775
00:49:10,140 --> 00:49:12,300
 Tu sam, tu sam.

776
00:49:12,300 --> 00:49:13,440
 Jesam daleko?

777
00:49:13,440 --> 00:49:15,440
 Ne, ne.

778
00:49:17,320 --> 00:49:19,480
 Samo hrabro vidim oko vas,

